commit.message:
[rs6000] Enable 32bit support for tests of x86-compatibile intrinsics

Also, bugfix for mmx-packuswb-1.c, which had ommitted the required
"-mpower8-vector" from dg-options.

2018-10-26  Paul A. Clarke  <pc@us.ibm.com>
